UID:381172c6-3881-5300-ae4e-f189768e392a
SUMMARY:European Commission Consultation on AudioVisual Media Legislation
DESCRIPTION:The European Commission is asking stakeholders -worldwide\, not limited 
 to EU Member States- to collect in-depth evidence\, information\, data a
 nd feedback from stakeholders on the impact of the current AVMSD and its
  planned review. We encourage you to contribute to the consultation\, ta
 king into account the Internet Society Policy Briefs on IP Blocking and 
 Mandated DNS Blocking.
URL:https://ec.europa.eu/info/law/better-regulation/have-your-say/initiatives/15752-Audiovisual-media-services-evaluation-and-update-of-EU-rules/public-consultation_en
DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260501
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260501
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7ef86a19-785d-5948-b203-0bc0b2c377b1
SUMMARY:European Summer School on Internet Governance (EuroSSIG)
DESCRIPTION:The 2026 Summer School offers a unique multidisciplinary high-level 48-h
 our academic programme. The programme is a balanced mixture of theoretic
 al lectures with world leading academics as well as practical presentati
 ons from well-known experts working directly in the technical community\
 , the market or in policy making organisations.
URL:https://eurossig.eu/eurossig/2026-edition/call-for-applications/
DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260331
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260331
END:VEVENT
